How Automation Testing improves productivity and competitiveness of a company

* Faster Feedback 
	* Automated testing assures higher efficiency of the development team. It also improves communication among coders, designers, and product owners that allows potential glitches to be immediately retified. 

*Accelerated Results
 	* Plenty of time is saved while using automated testing. This allows for testing to be carried out repeatedly, delivering faster results each time with lesser effort and time. 

